usage: renep <title> <season> <files>...
   or:  renep --help

   Renames the specified episode files to the following format:
     <title> <season>x<episode>

  options:
    -h, --help: displays help

  examples:
    renep "Kill la Kill (2013)" 1 *.mkv

    produces:
      Kill la Kill (2013) 01x01
      Kill la Kill (2013) 01x02
      ...
      Kill la Kill (2013) 01x24
